# README

## Local Development

*Locally serving the GitHub Pages documentation:*
> cd docs && bundle install && bundle exec jekyll serve --livereload

*Installing plugins:*
> sudo gem install jekyll-mermaid
> bundle add kramdown-syntax-coderay

Endpoint: <http://127.0.0.1:4000/yasmine-stationxml-editor/>

